execute as @a at @s run function roguecraft:shops/progressive/tell_main

execute as @e[type=minecraft:interaction,tag=ability_shop] at @s on attacker run function roguecraft:shops/ability/main with entity @e[distance=..2,type=marker,sort=nearest,limit=1] data
execute as @e[type=minecraft:interaction,tag=ability_shop] at @s on target run function roguecraft:shops/ability/main with entity @e[distance=..2,type=marker,sort=nearest,limit=1] data
execute as @a at @s run function roguecraft:shops/ability/tell_main

